Title: The magnetic phase diagram of dilute Cr-Ge alloys from electrical resistivity measurements at ambient and high pressure

Abstract: Measurements of the electrical resistivity of a series of dilute Cr-Ge alloys have revealed a new resistivity anomaly at the incommensurate-commensurate SDW phase transition of alloys with c>0.4 at% Ge. Pressure effects on the magnetic transitions are also reported.
